OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FThe King and Queen said they have left
OL,7,Fa piece of their heart behind in the
OL,8,FUnited States in a message to the
OL,9,Fnation's people.
OL,11,FCharles and Camilla's four-day state
OL,12,Fvisit to the US ended on Thursday with
OL,13,Fan overwhelmingly positive response
OL,14,Ffrom President Donald Trump, who
OL,15,Flifted tariffs on Scottish whisky.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
