OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777633372
OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FIn a message posted to social media,
OL,7,Fthe couple said: "Farewell and thank
OL,8,Fyou for the warmth of your welcome and
OL,9,Fthe kind support you gave us
OL,10,Fthroughout our first visit to the US
OL,11,Fas King and Queen, in this, your
OL,12,Fspecial anniversary year.
OL,14,F"We leave a piece of our (heart emoji)
OL,15,Fbehind and take a little of yours back
OL,16,Fhome with us. Until the next time...
OL,17,FGod Bless America."
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
