OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777633372
OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FThe message included a new image of
OL,7,Fthe royal couple at Blair House, the
OL,8,Fpresident's guest house opposite the
OL,9,FWhite House, where they stayed during
OL,10,Fthe visit.
OL,12,FCharles and Camilla, who travelled to
OL,13,Fcelebrate the 250th anniversary of
OL,14,FAmerican independence, were pictured
OL,15,Fgazing into each other's eyes while
OL,16,Fstanding in the Jackson Place sitting
OL,17,Froom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
