FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777633372
OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FThe Manhattan skyline, featuring the
OL,7,FStatue of Liberty and the Empire State
OL,8,FBuilding lit up, appeared in another
OL,9,Fpicture.
OL,11,FMr Trump said it was Charles and
OL,12,FCamilla's intervention that prompted
OL,13,Fthe decision to lift the tariffs on
OL,14,FScottish whisky, announced soon after
OL,15,Fthey said their goodbyes at the end of
OL,16,Ftheir state visit.
OL,18,FMark Kent, chief executive of the
OL,19,FScotch Whisky Association, said
OL,20,F"distillers can breathe a little
OL,21,Feasier" following the move.
OL,26,@|D@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
