SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777633372
OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FThe development will vindicate Downing
OL,7,FStreet's decision to send the King on
OL,8,Fa trip, viewed by some as highly
OL,9,Frisky, to repair the UK-US special
OL,10,Frelationship.
OL,12,FMr Trump said in a social media post
OL,13,Fthat while "people have wanted to do
OL,14,Fthis for a long time" the King and
OL,15,FQueen "got me to do something that
OL,16,Fnobody else was able to do".
OL,26,@uD@LOUvD@UO]wD@GOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
