OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FAt the end of the US visit, the King
OL,7,Fjetted off to Bermuda for a solo three-
OL,8,Fday tour.
OL,10,FArriving at LF Wade International
OL,11,FAirport at dusk, the UK Government's
OL,12,FVIP Airbus plane flew the Royal
OL,13,FStandard and Bermuda flag from the
OL,14,Fcockpit window.
OL,16,FCharles was greeted by Governor of
OL,17,FBermuda Andrew Murdoch and the Premier
OL,18,Fof Bermuda, David Burt and his wife
OL,19,FKristin, with a small guard of honour
OL,20,Fformed by the Royal Bermuda Regiment
OL,21,Fstanding to attention nearby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
