OL,3,CCharles and Camilla tell US 'thank you
OL,4,Cfor the warmth of your welcome'
OL,6,FThe formalities were low-key, as the
OL,7,FKing will receive a ceremonial welcome
OL,8,Fof pomp and pageantry featuring a 21-
OL,9,Fgun salute on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
